{
  "id": "EUVD-2026-29426",
  "enisaUuid": "6c2db5be-744e-3d3f-b202-1d0f30d00228",
  "description": "Affected devices do not properly validate and sanitize PLC/station name rendered on the \"communication\" parameters page of the web interface.\r\nThis could allow an authenticated attacker who is authorized to download a TIA project into the product, to inject malicious scripts into the page.\r\nIf a benign user with appropriate rights accesses the \"communication\" parameters page, the malicious code would be executed in the scope of their web session.",
